thread.title: THE OTHER SIDE

title: THE OTHER SIDE
text:
Only registered TrekEarth members may write critiques. Photographer's Note 
I visited this same area some time after and got another view of the same waterfall shown yesterday. This time I was in the other side of the creek and you can see the waters falling in front. Visitei esta mesma área algum tempo depois de ter tirado a foto postada ontem. Aqui vemos a vista da mesma cachoeira, mas do outro lado do riacho. Podem ver aqui a água caindo de frente. 
Nobody has marked this note useful
